      • wrapper

        public static Function<EventDAO,UserEventDAO> wrapper()

        A function that wraps an event DAO in a prefetching user event DAO. If the DAO already implements UserEventDAO, it is returned unwrapped.

        Returns:
        A wrapper function to make user event DAOs from event DAOs.
